I '''Gandhiskri shkola''' [[Zvolen]]ostar si oxto bershenge [[romani]] shkola (gimnaziyum). Lako anav del pativ le [[Gandhi]]skre, butshundo [[desi]] andar o 20to [[shelbersh]]. Kathe, shirdindoi [[Septembra]] [[2004]] [[bersh]]estar, siklen ćhave thai rakle (e palutne si opretele 30% [http://www1.umn.edu/humanrts/hrcommittee/slovakia2005.html]). Le siklovne, avri la shkolatar, beshen ando studentengro kher (internatos).

Le siklyaripnaske [[ćhiba]] si [[romani]], [[slovaika]] thai [[anglezikani]]. Siklel pes vi o [[romanipen]], o romano sanskrtipen.

